# qing_censorate_venal (via the qing_censorate.6 trampoline) then opens THIS window; every row is one
# venal official ranked most-corrupt-first, and clicking a name impeaches HIM (qing_censorate_impeach_
# selected) and closes the window. A clone of qing_justice_accuse_window (the Accuse picker the user
# asked this to mirror), dispatching the impeachment instead of a charge.
