# differ. The favour panel button refreshes the list (qing_harem.4 trampoline) then opens this; a
# row-click favours the chosen consort and closes the window. Rows keep the CHARACTER datacontext
# (no ScriptedGui override on the button) so the child [Character.Get*] reads resolve — see the #8
# marriage-window fix + imp19c_windows.gui:90.
